thread.title: CANADA STOCKS-TSX ends up ahead of Fed
thread.title_full: CANADA STOCKS-TSX ends up ahead of Fed | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: CANADA STOCKS-TSX ends up ahead of Fed
text:
TORONTO, Sept 15 Canada's main stock index ended higher on Tuesday in a broad but shallow rally as investors braced for a closely watched U.S. Federal Reserve rate decision this week.
The Toronto Stock Exchange's S&P/TSX composite index unofficially closed up 109.37 points, or 0.82 percent, at 13,462.71. All 10 main sectors rose, with utilities jumping 2.5 percent. (Reporting by Alastair Sharp ; Editing by Meredith Mazzilli)
